long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Have you ever wished you could change a traffic light? NowтАЩs your chance! In Traffic Command, you are the ULTIMATE traffic commander. You will have full control of traffic lights, but watch out, if you miss a red light, there will be serious trouble for the drivers! Good luck!

You can also play other categories game.

Game Instructions
Tap the GREEN light, and Tap to Play to start. You are now in control of ALL traffic lights!

In each level, tap each traffic light to go from RED to GREEN. Your goal is to move traffic safely across the intersection. As cars safely move through the intersection, you will earn dollars. You must be a quick or the cars will CRASH! Once youтАЩve completed your level, you will move up!

Good luck and have fun Traffic Commander!
